videoSnippet.title: Attention! It's Fabi vs Shakh | Batumi Chess Olympiad (2018)
videoSnippet.description:
Follow me on Instagram for extra content: https://www.instagram.com/agadmator/

Fabiano Caruana vs Shakhriyar Mamedyarov
43rd Chess Olympiad (2018), rd 8, Oct-2 
Spanish Game: Morphy Defense (C83)

1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 a6 4. Ba4 Nf6 5. O-O Nxe4 6. d4 b5 7. Bb3 d5 8. dxe5 Be6 9. Nbd2 Nc5 10. c3 Be7 11. Bc2 d4 12. Nb3 d3 13. Bb1 Nxb3 14. axb3 Bf5 15. Be3 O-O 16. Bd4 Qd5 17. Re1 d2 18. Re2 Bxb1 19. Rxb1 Nxd4 20. Nxd4 Bg5 21. g3 c5 22. Nf5 Qd3 23. Nd6 Qg6 24. h4 Bf4 25. Ne4 f5 26. Nxd2 Rad8 27. Ra1 Rfe8 28. Qe1 Bxd2 29. Rxd2 Rxd2 30. Qxd2 Rxe5 31. Qd8+ Re8 32. Qd5+ Qe6 33. Rd1 c4 34. bxc4 bxc4 35. Qb7 Re7 36. Rd8+ Kf7 37. Qf3 g6 38. Qf4 Qc6 39. Rd1 Re4 40. Qh6 Kg8 41. h5 Re8 42. hxg6 hxg6 43. Kf1 Re6 44. Qh4 Re8 45. Rd4 Rc8 46. Qh6 Qe6 47. Rh4 Kf7 48. Qh7+ Kf6 49. Rd4 Qe7 50. Qh6 Kf7 51. Qd2 Rc7 52. Rh4 Kf6 53. Qd4+ Qe5 54. Qb6+ Kg7 55. Qb8 Kf6 56. Qh8+ Ke6 57. Qg8+ Kf6 58. Rd4 Qe7 59. Rd8 Kg5 60. f4+ Kh5 61. Rd2 Qg7 62. Rh2+ Kg4 63. Kg2 g5 64. Qe8
